relation: After shovelling the snow four times on the same day, I got the idea for this little number.
A Mr. Saturn feeling happy about himself over his creation. I drew this one back in the winter months of 2011.
He will consume your souuuuulll...or, he'll possess it, at any rate.
Whose idea was it to go through this tunnel, again? Aw, nuts.
